Come see this 3 bedroom, two bath, open floor plan home in the beautiful Tierra Del Este area! 
**There is a tenant at this property, so please allow at least 2 hours notice! **
**Please schedule an appointment on Showing Time, and please do not disturb tenant. Pets present and contained in kennels in the home.**
 Open floor plan, large kitchen and breakfast area with lovely windows and natural light. Large back yard with lots of potential, and a beautiful neighborhood! This home will not last!  REFRIGERATOR WILL CONVEY
